  { question: 'How many treatments are needed for complete tattoo removal?', answer: 'Generally 6-12 treatments are needed, but this depends on the tattoo size, colors, age and quality of the ink used. Permanent makeup tattoos can usually be removed with fewer treatments.' },
  { question: 'How painful is laser tattoo removal?', answer: 'Thanks to our cold hammer cooling technique, the treatment is noticeably less painful than traditional methods. Most of our clients feel only a mild stinging sensation.' },
