            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-5 text-base leading-relaxed">
              Laser tattoo removal is safe, virtually painless, and when performed by an expert with high-quality equipment, <strong>the results can be complete</strong>.
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6 text-base leading-relaxed">
